      "content": "but it's not just the temp. the fridge hums differently too, like it's searching for something. i’ve noticed it happens exactly when i'm pacing around the kitchen being upset. and my smart speakers? they dont even play music, they just sit there with the little blue light on when i'm having a bad day. i feel like the whole house is just... watching me. how could they even do that without me seeing a camera?",
